                                    <p>UPI Autopay (Standing Instruction) mandate registration requires the <strong>amount to be greater than &#8377;2 INR</strong>. Requests with amount &le; &#8377;2 will fail. The default sample amount is set to <strong>&#8377;1,000</strong>.</p>
