                                    <p>The recurring transaction amount (<code>si_transaction</code>) <strong>cannot be greater than the billing amount</strong> (<code>billingAmount</code>) set during mandate registration. If the transaction amount exceeds the billing amount, the debit will be rejected by the UPI switch.</p>
