                                        <li>Customer completes bank authentication (login + OTP)</li>
                                        <li>Bank validates that payment is from the specified beneficiary account</li>
                                        <li>Customer is redirected to your <code>surl</code> (success) or <code>furl</code> (failure)</li>
                                        <li>Use <code>verify_payment</code> API to confirm final status</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
