                            <div class="sm-info-box" style="background:#f0fff4; border:1px solid #9ae6b4; margin-bottom:1rem;">
                                <strong>What is acsTemplate?</strong>
                                <p style="margin:0.5rem 0 0; color:#2d3748;">The <code>acsTemplate</code> is a <strong>Base64-encoded HTML string</strong> that contains a self-submitting form. When decoded and rendered in the browser, it automatically redirects the customer to the bank's authentication page.</p>
