                                    <strong>UDF Hash Rule:</strong> udf1 through udf5 are part of hash calculation. Even if sent as empty strings, they must be present in the hash formula:<br>
                                    <code style="background:#e2e8f0; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:3px;">sha512(key|txnid|amount|productinfo|firstname|email|udf1|udf2|udf3|udf4|udf5||||||SALT)</code>
                                </div>
