                                <li><strong>pg=ENACH:</strong> Must use ENACH as payment gateway type (not NB)</li>
                                <li><strong>beneficiarydetail:</strong> Mandatory for Net Banking - contains customer's bank account details</li>
                                <li><strong>bankcode:</strong> Use eNACH-specific bank codes (e.g., ICICENCC, HABORENCC, SBIENCC)</li>
                                <li>The <code>mihpayid</code> from callback becomes your <code>authpayuid</code></li>
                                <li>Mandate activation can take 24-48 hours after customer authorization</li>
